Ingredients

1.5 lbs ground beef
1.5 lbs sausage
3 cans stewed tomatoes
2 cans kidney beans(rinsed)
1 cup chopped onion
1 large green pepper
1 can tomato paste 6oz
2 jalepeno's
2 tblsp chili powder
2 tblsp white vinegar
1 tblsp spicy brown mustard
1 tblsp oregano
2 garlic cloves, minced
1.5 tsp ground cumin
1.5 tsp hot sauce
1 tsp salt
1 tsp paprika

optional: sour cream, shredded cheese, saltines

Notes: Leave out peppers/hotsauce if too spicy

Directions:
In dutch oven combine meats and brown, then drain. Add remaining ingredients, bring to a boil. Then reduce heat and simmer for 30 mins
